Idols SA host and rapper Proverb spoilt himself with a fancy new Porsche Cayenne GTS that is estimated to be worth over R1.4-million. Taking to Instagram Proverb shared pictures of his sexy new ride. The TV star could not hide his excitement as the massive achievement is no doubt a dream come true. Proverb also revealed that he took the new ride to show it to his dad, who was incredibly proud of him.